SEOUL, July 8 (Reuters) - Samsung Electro-Mechanics (009150.KS) said on Friday that it is in talks with Tesla Inc (TSLA.O) to possibly supply camera modules, but that it cannot reveal the deal size or amount at this time. Samsung Electro-Mechanics will continue to work on advancing and diversifying its camera modules, it added in a regulatory filing. Our Standards: The Thomson Reuters Trust Principles.